column6: Shallow long stairs from courtyard to locust walk in front of van pelt. Alternate route goes around building.
There are multiple steps on the walkway from College Green towards 36th street
The alternate route is a ramp between the Anneberg School of Communication and Public Policy Center which leads to Wlanut street. There is another ramp which leads to the Locust Walk.
A large construction project is blocking off this entry point to canvas
